'''Dominic M. Armato''' ([[18 November|November 18]], [[1976]]) is an American voice actor. He is best known as the voice of protagonist Guybrush Threepwood in LucasArts' ''[[wikipedia:Monkey Island (series)|Monkey Island]]'' games.
